data.description: Deputies responding to what they thought was a domestic disturbance ended up finding a human trafficking victim who had been assaulted at a Rancho Cucamonga hotel last week, authorities said Monday. data.title: Deputies Find Human Trafficking Victim While Responding to Disturbance at Rancho Cucamonga Hotel: Officials
